Name: assign_worker_to_team
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a worker is assigned to a team, 0 otherwise

Name: assign_team_to_project
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a team is assigned to a project, 0 otherwise

Name: assign_task_to_worker
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a task is assigned to a worker, 0 otherwise

Name: select_user_story_for_sprint
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a user story is selected for a sprint, 0 otherwise

Name: assign_feature_to_release
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a feature is included in a release plan, 0 otherwise

Name: set_feature_priority
Description: Integer variable for setting the priority of a feature

Name: set_project_budget
Description: Continuous variable for allocating budget to a project

Name: determine_sprint_duration_days
Description: Integer variable for the duration of a sprint in days

Name: assign_worker_to_role
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a worker takes on a specific role, 0 otherwise

Name: match_skill_to_task
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a worker with a required skill is assigned to a task, 0 otherwise

Name: set_task_effort_hours
Description: Integer variable for estimating the effort of a task in hours

Name: choose_sprint_goal
Description: Binary variable: 1 if a sprint goal is selected for a sprint, 0 otherwise
